#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Notify" field of the "Patron" table</h2>
This field contains an e-mail address which gives the system the ability to use
either text or e-mail notification to get bulletins to the patron.  For instance,
it might contain a traditional e-mail address:
<div class=field_format>dufflerpatron@yahoo.com</div>
or an address that it can send a text to:
<div class=field_format>nnnnnnnnnn@vtext.com (for Verizon customers)</div>
Currently, there is no ability to send mass bulletins (say, in the event of a snow storm) so this is unused.

